WEBVTT

00:00:03.170 --> 00:00:05.739
NARRATOR: While Lysandre's plan
to create his ideal world moves

00:00:05.739 --> 00:00:10.244
ahead, Clemont is attempting to
take back Prism Tower, Serena

00:00:10.244 --> 00:00:14.014
and Mairin are rescuing Chespie,
and Bonnie is chasing after

00:00:14.014 --> 00:00:16.383
Squishy. All of our heroes are
valiantly doing what they can.

00:00:18.485 --> 00:00:22.122
As for Ash and Greninja, they
have broken free from Lysandre's

00:00:22.122 --> 00:00:24.558
restraints and are about to
unleash their counterattack,

00:00:24.558 --> 00:00:26.059
alongside Alain.

00:00:31.899 --> 00:00:33.934
ASH: All right,
Noivern, use Boomburst!

00:00:33.934 --> 00:00:35.369
Now, Pikachu, Thunderbolt!

00:00:36.169 --> 00:00:38.205
NOIVERN: [BOOMBURST MOVE]

00:00:38.205 --> 00:00:40.774
PIKACHU: [THUNDERBOLT MOVE]

00:00:40.774 --> 00:00:42.442
LYSANDRE: Outnumbering
me is completely unimportant!

00:00:42.442 --> 00:00:44.177
Use Hyper Beam!

00:00:44.177 --> 00:00:45.279
MEGA GYARADOS: [HYPER BEAM MOVE]

00:00:46.179 --> 00:00:48.081
LYSANDRE: Now, Dragon Tail!

00:00:48.081 --> 00:00:49.983
MEGA GYARADOS:
[DRAGON TAIL MOVE]

00:00:49.983 --> 00:00:50.951
PIKACHU: [SHOCKED]
NOIVERN: [EFFORT]

00:00:52.286 --> 00:00:53.754
PIKACHU: [WORRIED]

00:00:53.754 --> 00:00:55.122
NOIVERN: [STUNNED]

00:00:55.122 --> 00:00:56.957
ASH: Noivern!

00:00:56.957 --> 00:00:59.359
HAWLUCHA: [CONCERNED]
NOIVERN: [REASSURING]

00:01:03.196 --> 00:01:04.765
ASH: Thanks a lot, Noivern!

00:01:04.765 --> 00:01:06.567
MEGA GYARADOS: [GROWLING]

00:01:07.234 --> 00:01:08.802
ALAIN: Use Dragon Claw!

00:01:08.802 --> 00:01:09.736
MEGA CHARIZARD:
[DRAGON CLAW MOVE]

00:01:09.736 --> 00:01:11.638
MEGA GYARADOS: [PAINED]

00:01:11.638 --> 00:01:13.707
ASH:
Hawlucha, use High Jump Kick!

00:01:13.707 --> 00:01:14.675
HAWLUCHA: [HIGH JUMP KICK MOVE]

00:01:16.843 --> 00:01:18.679
LYSANDRE: Catch it, quick!

00:01:18.679 --> 00:01:19.913
HAWLUCHA: [SHOCKED]

00:01:23.116 --> 00:01:24.551
ASH: Hawlucha!

00:01:24.551 --> 00:01:26.553
HAWLUCHA: [STUNNED]

00:01:28.055 --> 00:01:30.023
ASH: You were great, Hawlucha.
We'll take it from here.

00:01:32.659 --> 00:01:35.228
LYSANDRE: This power...the
power of Mega Evolution...

00:01:35.228 --> 00:01:37.497
MEGA GYARADOS: [ROARING]

00:01:37.497 --> 00:01:41.034
LYSANDRE: It only happens during
battle. It's a kind of battle

00:01:41.034 --> 00:01:43.904
instinct. Something Pokémon
forget after being in constant

00:01:43.904 --> 00:01:44.905
contact with humans.

00:01:47.441 --> 00:01:49.743
LYSANDRE: But when a
Pokémon unleashes its battle

00:01:49.743 --> 00:01:52.279
instinct...that's when
it gains Mega Evolution power!

00:01:53.313 --> 00:01:54.314
ALAIN: Stop it!
You've got it wrong!

00:01:55.349 --> 00:01:57.017
LYSANDRE: Only the victor can

00:01:57.017 --> 00:01:58.352
prove that
he's not wrong, Alain...

00:01:59.653 --> 00:02:01.755
LYSANDRE: Now, Hyper Beam!

00:02:01.755 --> 00:02:03.423
MEGA GYARADOS: [HYPER BEAM MOVE]

