00:02:08.662 --> 00:02:10.931
I've gotta get to Squishy!

00:02:10.931 --> 00:02:12.165
BLAZIKEN MASK:
Then what will you do?!

00:02:12.165 --> 00:02:14.134
BONNIE: I've gotta save Squishy!

00:02:14.134 --> 00:02:16.236
I promised I wouldn't
let it go ever, ever again!

00:02:16.236 --> 00:02:17.004
DEDENNE: [AFFIRMATIVE]

00:02:19.406 --> 00:02:20.774
BONNIE: Let go!
BLAZIKEN MASK: No, Bonnie!

00:02:30.083 --> 00:02:32.552
I stand tall
'Cause I know I'm a winner

